    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK700">
<l>paḻaiya meṉakkaruti paṇpalla ceyyuṅ</l>
<l>keḻutakaimai kēṭu tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The (foolish) claim with which a minister does unbecoming acts because of his (long) familiarity (with the king) will ensure his ruin.</l>
            </lg>
